<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="IE=edge">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>CERTIFICATE OF PARTICIPATION</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Rubik:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        @media  screen {
            .main-body{
                padding: 1rem 2rem;
                font-family: 'Rubik', sans-serif;
                background-image: url('https://demo1.lakhetech.com/themes-assets/certificate/final-bg1.jpg');
                background-size: 100%;
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
                background-size:cover;
                height: 90vh;
                box-shadow:0 14px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
                }
            }
        @media  print and (max-width:1215px) {
                .main-body{
                padding: 2rem 2rem;
                font-family: 'Rubik', sans-serif;
                background-image: url('https://demo1.lakhetech.com/themes-assets/certificate/final-bg1.jpg') !important;
                background-size: 100%;
                background-repeat: no-repeat;
                background-size:cover;
                background-position: center;
                box-shadow:0 14px 25px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.16);
                }
                .text{
                    
                    padding: 10px;
                }
                .text h1{
                color: #213970;
                margin: 0px; 
                }
            }
        @media  screen, print {
            .top-section{
                margin-bottom: 0px;
            }
            .text{
                text-align: center;
                margin-top: 0px;
            }
            .name{
                position: relative;
                text-decoration: underline black 1px;
            }
            .text h1{
                color: #213970;
                margin-bottom: 0px; 
            }
            .text p{
                font-size: 18px;
            }   
            .bold{
                font-weight:600;
                color: #C62026;
            }
           .u::after,.u1::after{
                content: "";
                position: absolute;
                background-color: black;
                height: 1px;
                bottom: -10px;
                right: 0;
            }
            .u,.u1{
                position: relative;
            }
            .u::after {
                width: 100%;
                left: 0rem;
            }
            .u1::after {
                width: 110px;
                left: -4px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="main-body">
        <div class="top-section">
            <center><img src="https://demo1.lakhetech.com/themes-assets/images/KM-15-logo.png" alt="logo" width="150px"></center>
        </div> 
        <div class="text" >
            <h1>CERTIFICATE OF PARTICIPATION</h1><br>
            <p class="top-text">This certificate is presented to</p>
            <p class="bold name" style="font-size: 25px;"> Lamar Madden</p>
            <p style="padding:0rem 2rem;">for participating in <span class="bold">Corporate Run</span> at New Marathon Indian Embassy held on 15th Dec, 2023. <br><br> Congratulations for your acheivement and thank you for your paticipation. </p>
            <div style="margin-top: 2rem;">
                <p style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><span class="u" > 2020/02/03</span><span class="u1" style="margin-left: 19rem;"><img src="https://demo1.lakhetech.com/themes-assets/certificate/signature.png" alt="sign" width="90px" height="60px"></span></p>
                <p  style="margin-top: 0rem; padding-left:25px ;"> Date <span style="margin-left: 22rem;">Signature</span>   </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>